review_data.title: Hidden Vietnam in the heart of Zürich
review_data.content: The restaurant was absolutely lovely with very fast service. The taste of the food was incredible and reasonably priced. Will definitely come back again.

review_data.title: Great well prices Vietnamsese just on the river
review_data.content: Good food, fairly priced for Zurich, and somewhat akin to what you would get in VN (somewhat) - its has not been made too Swiss - big win :) Having lived in Asia this was a welcome find! Would def come again on next visit...More
